setDetails.setDescription: Invest into the long-term success of innovative projects grown by the excellent Ethereum community. This index assumes that ETH 2.0 will be a success and L2s will co-exist and scale into fit-for-purpose niches. Some Metaverse tokens from other chains and BTC is added for diversification.
